title: Phins beat Bills, Brady vs Rodgers
description:
Jalen and Jacoby discuss the big Phins win over the Bills. Jacoby is always there for the Bills Mafia, but was it rare mistakes by the Bills or great play by the Dolphins that caused the Buffalo loss? Listen as the guys give their opinion. Plus, Brady vs Rodgers was not what everyone expected. It was the defense that stepped it up for both teams. Is Brady missing Gronk or is this normal for Brady to struggle a few games in the season? Chiefs get surprised by the Colts. Not the weekend Patrick Mahomes wanted. Find out what needs to change for Kansas City. Also, Rihanna Super Bowl Halftime performer? Sign us up.
